check ExperimentalData

check_experiment.Rd

check ExperimentalData

Usage

check_experiment(x, cg = NULL)

Arguments

x

a tibble containing ExperimentalData, with an ID column and a date of SAMPLE (not date of assay).

cg

the chronogram to join

Value

"valid" or stop with message
